workflow.name: Auto-upload Instagram videos to YouTube with GPT-4o and Google Sheets tracking
workflow.description:
## üìä Description
Automate your cross-platform publishing workflow by automatically uploading Instagram videos to YouTube with AI-optimized titles and tags. üöÄüé¨ This workflow runs every six hours, fetches newly posted Instagram videos, checks Google Sheets to avoid duplicate uploads, generates SEO-ready YouTube metadata using GPT-4o, downloads the video in high quality, uploads it to YouTube, and logs the full upload details for tracking. Perfect for creators, agencies, and businesses managing multi-platform content distribution at scale. üìà‚ú®

## üîÅ What This Template Does
1Ô∏è‚É£ Runs every 6 hours to fetch recent Instagram media via Graph API. ‚è∞
 2Ô∏è‚É£ Splits the media list and filters for today‚Äôs video posts only. üé•
 3Ô∏è‚É£ Checks Google Sheets to see if the video was already uploaded. üîé
 4Ô∏è‚É£ Sends Instagram caption to AI to generate:
 ‚Äî a YouTube-optimized title (max 60 chars)
 ‚Äî SEO-friendly tags extracted from text + hashtags
 5Ô∏è‚É£ Downloads the Instagram video binary file. ‚¨áÔ∏è
 6Ô∏è‚É£ Waits 3 seconds to avoid YouTube rate limits. ‚è≥
 7Ô∏è‚É£ Uploads the video to YouTube with:
 ‚Äî title
 ‚Äî tags
 ‚Äî caption as description
 8Ô∏è‚É£ Logs the upload details into Google Sheets (ID, title, link, date, status). üìä
 9Ô∏è‚É£ Prevents future duplicate uploads using a spreadsheet lookup. ‚úîÔ∏è

## ‚≠ê Key Benefits
‚úÖ Fully automates Instagram ‚Üí YouTube video publishing
 ‚úÖ AI-generated metadata increases YouTube visibility & search ranking
 ‚úÖ Duplicate upload prevention ensures clean channel management
 ‚úÖ Tracks upload history in a Google Sheet for transparency
 ‚úÖ Requires zero manual downloading, editing, or re-uploading
 ‚úÖ Ideal for creators, brands, community managers & agencies

## üß© Features
- Instagram Business API media fetch
- Filter for today‚Äôs videos using timestamps
- Google Sheets duplicate checker
- GPT-4o caption analysis for metadata generation
- Structured JSON output for reliable AI parsing
- YouTube video upload with custom metadata
- Spreadsheet logging with append/update
- Automatic scheduling with cron trigger
- Full workflow batching & safe retry logic

## üîê Requirements
- Facebook Graph API credentials (Instagram Business Account)
- YouTube OAuth2 credentials
- OpenAI API key (GPT-4o)
- Google Sheets OAuth2 credentials
- A Google Spreadsheet for tracking uploaded videos
- Instagram Business Account ID + Access Token

## üéØ Target Audience
- Social media creators & influencers
- Digital marketing agencies
- YouTube automation teams
- Brands repurposing Instagram content for YouTube
- Content managers handling multiple accounts
- Community managers needing hands-free cross-posting

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
